deps.context:
project(fluffos
        description "fluffos lpc driver"
        languages c cxx)

libs.content:
find_program(mysql_config_executable
      names
      mysql_config
      doc
      "full path of mysql_config"
      paths
      ${_exe_fallback_path}
      )

find_library(mbedtls_library
             names mbedtls
             path_suffixes lib library
             hints ${mbedtls_root_dir}
             no_cmake_find_root_path)

find_library(mbedtls_crypto_library
             names mbedcrypto
             path_suffixes lib library
             hints ${mbedtls_root_dir}
             no_cmake_find_root_path)

find_library(mbedtls_x509_library
             names mbedx509
             path_suffixes lib library
             hints ${mbedtls_root_dir}
             no_cmake_find_root_path)

find_program(rpmtools_rpmbuild_executable
    names rpmbuild
    paths "/usr/bin;/usr/lib/rpm"
    path_suffixes bin
    doc "the rpm builder tool")

find_program(git_executable ${git_names}
  paths
    "c:/program files/git/bin"
    "c:/program files (x86)/git/bin"
  doc "git command line client")

find_program(openssl_executable openssl openssl.exe bin/openssl.exe
		hints ${_openssl_root_hints}
		path 
			/usr/bin/ 
			bin/
	  	doc "openssl executable")

find_library ( miniz_libraries libminiz.so libminiz.a libminiz.so.2 libminiz.so.0.1
    /usr/local/lib
    /usr/local/lib64
    /usr/lib
    /usr/lib64
)
